     <h2>About Langzhong ancient</h2>
     <p>Lang in the ancient city, is the <em>national AAAAA-class tourist</em> attractions, 
the Millennium ancient county, the Chinese culture of the Spring Festival, one of China's four ancient cities.<br /><br /> 
Langzhong ancient city is located in the northeastern edge of the Sichuan Basin, the middle reaches of the Jialing River,
Langzhong ancient city "5A" scenic area of 4.59 square kilometers, the core area of the ancient city of 2 square kilometers. 
As of 2015, the ancient city has more than 2,300 years of history of the city, for the ancient city of Pakistan Shu military.
Langzhong ancient city has Zhang Fei Temple, Yongan Temple, Wulong Temple, Tengwangge, Guanyin Temple, Baba Temple, the Great Buddha Temple, 
North Sichuan Road Gongyuan 8 national key cultural relics protection units; Shaojiawan grave, pen tower, stone temple cliff Statues, Raytheon cliff statues, Niu Wang hole cliff statues, 
the Red Fourth Army General Political Department site, Huaguang and other 22 provincial cultural relics protection units. February 2010 Langzhong City won the "Chinese Spring Festival culture" title;
in September 2013,Langzhong ancient city tourist area was approved as the national <strong>5A-class tourist attractions</strong>.</p>
