     <h2>Han Huan Hou Temple</h2>
     <p><strong>Zhang Fei</strong> for the Three Kingdoms Shu Han, "Five Tigers will be" one, <strong>Liu Bei</strong> captured in Sichuan,
the closure of the fly for the generals of the general manager of the captain, and any Brazilian prince guarding Langzhong.
In the guard Langzhong 7 years, Zhang Fei security of the people, the development of agricultural mulberry.<br /><br />
Zhang Yu first year (AD 221), Zhang Fei was under the Zhang, Fan Qiang harm, posthumous as Huan Hou,
buried in Langzhong. Zhang Fei, after the people who respect their loyalty, for his building mound built temple, 
to commemorate, from the beginning when the Han Huan Hou Temple has been 1700 years of history.<br /><br />
According to Langzhou provincial governor Cui Shan "new Brazilian prefect Zhang Huan Hou Temple in mind," 
Zhang Fei died after the construction of Huan Hou Temple, although the soldiers were destroyed by fire, but tired to build,
"soil more than a few, the pasture. Ming Dynasty meal Li heavy, surrounded by graves in the building 47 feet.<br /><br />
Since then there are many renewals. Today's Huan Hou Temple for the Ming and Qing Dynasties to rebuild the four-style courtyard-style
ancient buildings, covering over 5,000 square meters, large-scale, beautifully built by the gate, enemy million floor, 
around the arch, east and west rooms, hall, Tombs, tombs, construction area of
2200 square meters, for the three countries a major cultural heritage.</p>
